OL,5,G0100 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,6,     FVera's drinking almost gets her
OL,7,     Farrested in a pub, and Helen
OL,8,     FMasters cons everyone to win her
OL,9,     Facquittal, then gives an
OL,10,     Fincendiary interview to the media.
OL,11,G0205 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,12,     FThe Governor introduces a
OL,13,     Fvolleyball program to let the
OL,14,     Finmates work off their tension.
OL,15,     FDoug gets out of jail and turns up
OL,16,     Fat the Warner farm to see Lynn.
OL,17,G0305 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,18,     FKaren talks Franky down from the
OL,19,     Froof and offers to teach her how
OL,20,     Fto read. Back in the city, Lynn
OL,21,     Fand Doug move in with his friends
OL,22,     FBernie and Suz.
